practitioner.about:
Dr. Maisa Zobeidi is a General Dental Practitioner at the Al Zahia and Al Taawun branch of Medcare Medical Centre. She completed her Bachelor of Dental Surgery (BDS) from the University of Sharjah and is currently studying to obtain a Master’s degree in fixed and removable prosthodontics from King's College London.

Dr. Zobeidi has spent more than a decade in her chosen field and is a dedicated dentist with a passion for providing exceptional patient care. After her internship, she became a Clinical Tutor with the University Dental Hospital, Sharjah followed by a short stint with Bright White Dental Center. She then worked with the Oxygen Medical Center and Basmat Al Hayat Medical Center, Sharjah as a General Dentist. She also worked as a Dental Practitioner with Zulekha Hospital in Sharjah and DentaMed Clinic, in Dubai before joining Medcare.

Her expertise covers the entire gamut of preventive dentistry including dental cleanings, fluoride treatments and sealants, restorative dentistry including fillings, crowns, bridges, dentures and root canal therapy, cosmetic dentistry including teeth whitening, veneers and smile makeovers, periodontal care including treatment of gum disease, paediatric dentistry, emergency dentistry, TMJ problems and full mouth rehabilitation for tooth wear cases. She has successfully treated patients with cavities, Gingivitis, tooth sensitivity, toothaches, bad breath, tooth erosion, teeth grinding and oral infections. She has a special interest in cosmetic dentistry and smile enhancement procedures. She is proficient in managing fixed prosthodontics like dental crowns, dental bridges, ceramic Inlays and Onlays and removable prosthodontics including complete and partial dentures. She is adept at managing dental emergencies as well as preventive dentistry and oral cancer screening. She believes in staying abreast of the latest advancements in dentistry through renowned journals and takes a keen interest in the application of AI in healthcare as a potential for the future of dental care.

She is fluent in Arabic, Persian, and English with an intermediate proficiency in French. In her spare time, she enjoys reading, creating educational content for social media and volunteering.

locations.about: Medcare Medical Centre in Al Zahia stands as a premium, advanced healthcare facility devoted to meeting the diverse healthcare needs of its community. This inviting medical centre prioritizes comfort and convenience, providing cuttingedge facilities and comprehensive medical services all under one roof. Ideal for patients of every age seeking precise diagnoses and prompt treatment across various specialties. At the helm of Medcare Medical Centre Al Zahia is a team of multicultural, multilingual doctors, complemented by exceptionally-trained and experienced nurses and medical staff. The centre takes pride in its extensive array of stateof-the-art equipment, empowering its highly skilled medical team to deliver a premium level of care to all patients. Experience the warmth of family-centric care delivered by our highly talented medical and non-medical staff. At Medcare Medical Centre Al Zahia, we offer a range of services, including Internal Medicine, Gynaecology, Paediatrics, Dermatology & Aesthetics, ENT, Dentistry, Orthopaedics and Physiotherapy. As part of our commitment to accessible healthcare, Medcare operates a network of four hospitals and 20 plus multi-specialty clinics across Dubai and Sharjah. Our goal is to provide reliable and timely medical care to our diverse clientele. Great News! We are expending to better suit all your medical and beauty needs!
